doing, all the fancy new stuff it's because
of ball bearings. If you look in a yo-yo,

00:00:19.650 --> 00:00:24.949
you've got a ball bearing. This is a ball
bearing roller, it goes in the center of the

00:00:24.949 --> 00:00:29.860
yo-yo itself and this is actually what the
string goes around onto it. I'll show really

00:00:29.860 --> 00:00:35.940
