inside here you've got all these little balls
and actually this is all some of the factory

00:00:41.180 --> 00:00:44.960
lubricant that comes in there to help keep
the rust out, but you'll notice all these

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:49.949
little balls go in there and what happens
is these spin around, that's what the yo-yo

00:00:49.949 --> 00:00:55.440
is on to. And as the yo-yo is spinning around
this, because of all those little balls, you've

